law.text:
** TAKES EFFECT JULY 1, 2013 PER CHAPTER 674 OF 2012 **
In this subtitle the following words have the meanings indicated.
"Act" means Chapter 674 (S.B._____/H.B. 713) (2lr1169/2lr1648) of the Acts of the General Assembly of 2012.
"Pre-effective-date financing statement" means a financing statement filed before the effective date of the Act.
